title: Weekly Review with Clay and Buck H1 - Feb 5 2022
itunes:title: Weekly Review with Clay and Buck H1 - Feb 5 2022
description:
California Governor Gavin Newsom and celebrity friends enjoy NFC Championship game in L.A. unmasked. "Next week in L.A. is going to be the Super Bowl, and I believe it is going to be the Super Bowl of all hypocrisies," Clay predicted. Trudeau tests positive for covid, still negative for testosterone, notes Buck. Leftists attack Canadian anti-mandate trucker convoy, like everything they disagree with, suggest truckers sponsored by Russia. Poll: 76% disagree with Biden's SCOTUS quota. Apple adds pregnant man emoji.
